@8060 = ~The Sly Sword~
@8061 = ~Also known as Kingslayer, this sword saw extensive use in the civil war which devastated the kingdom of Tethyr and annihilated much of Tethyr's royal family. It has since changed owners a number of times, most recently having been in the possession of an assassin belonging to the Cult of the Dragon.

