@13000 = ~Ichor +2~
@13001 = ~This throwing dagger is no ordinary weapon. With a finely crafted, double-edged blade, it is designed for precision and lethality. Its compact handle offers perfect balance, making it a deadly tool in the hands of a skilled assassin. Coated with a potent, dark poison known only to the most feared killers, it is capable of bringing even the mightiest paladin to their knees. Rare and difficult to obtain, this dagger is the weapon of choice for those who seek to strike down even the most powerful foes from the shadows.

STATISTICS:

