@13004 = ~Thunderclap +3~
@13005 = ~The Thunderclap is a dagger of strange and unpredictable power, its blade shimmering with the faintest crackle of arcane energy. Forged in forgotten times by a sect of storm-worshiping priests, this weapon is said to channel the fury of a divine tempest. One moment it is in your grasp, the next it seems to vanish, only to reappear with a deadly strike.

When the dagger is drawn, the air seems to hum with energy, and its edge leaves a faint echo of thunder in the wake of each strike. Though it is a simple weapon, its true strength lies in the storm it can summon—shocking enemies with the force of a distant storm's rage.

STATISTICS:

Combat abilities:
– +1/2 attacks per round
– +25% electrical resistance
– Teleport Strike: When thrown and the dagger strikes a target, the wielder is instantly teleported to the target's location

