 3 Strength

Weight: 0~

@13005 = ~Iceberg +4~
@13006 = ~This peculiar weapon is less a dagger than it is a solid mass of enchanted ice, its crystalline form resembling a jagged shard more than a finely crafted blade. The Icerberg is cold to the touch, exuding a supernatural chill that causes frost to form on the ground beneath it. When wielded by a strong hand, the icy blade hums with latent arcane power, its cold edge capable of rending flesh and bone with unnatural ease.

Though cumbersome for the weak, those who possess the strength to bear it will find that the Icerberg can be wielded with deadly precision. Upon striking, it releases a burst of freezing energy, capable of temporarily immobilizing foes and causing frostbite that lingers long after the blow is struck. In the hands of a truly powerful warrior, the Icerberg is as formidable as any sword, though its unusual nature makes it difficult to master.

STATISTICS:

Combat abilities:
– 25% chance to cause Slow on hit for 10 seconds. Creatures immune to cold are also immune to this effect

THACO: +4
